WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.066 --> 00:00:05.666
This girl is so handsome.

2
00:00:05.666 --> 00:00:08.833
Together with my family.

3
00:00:08.933 --> 00:00:09.700
Right.

4
00:00:09.700 --> 00:00:13.000
I have to make a good impression on my niece.

5
00:00:22.200 --> 00:00:25.666
Grandma, is your health better?

6
00:00:25.666 --> 00:00:28.366
Oh, I'm so upset.

7
00:00:28.366 --> 00:00:30.166
Oh my God.

8
00:00:30.366 --> 00:00:32.566
Can't eat or sleep

9
00:00:32.566 --> 00:00:35.566
Every day I think of my wife.

10
00:00:35.766 --> 00:00:37.100
Granddaughter-in-law.

11
00:00:37.100 --> 00:00:39.300
Oh, my niece-in-law is here.

12
00:00:39.900 --> 00:00:41.800
Grandma, my name is Uncle Luu.

13
00:00:41.800 --> 00:00:43.200
Is your niece-in-law.

14
00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:45.266
Let me take a closer look.

15
00:00:51.266 --> 00:00:54.833
Grandma couldn't eat or sleep

16
00:00:56.666 --> 00:00:58.500
I only ate two small bites.

17
00:00:58.500 --> 00:00:59.566
Furthermore.

18
00:00:59.566 --> 00:01:01.933
That old lady was sick and couldn't eat.

19
00:01:01.933 --> 00:01:03.566
I see that you are an ungrateful descendant.

20
00:01:03.566 --> 00:01:05.433
You want to starve the old lady?

21
00:01:05.733 --> 00:01:07.166
It's still my fault.